{'id': 10657967, 'body': 'Hi njxjejx. 

If you are a minor, you need parental consent to upgrade your account. If you are of legal age, you can use your Student ID, plus a secondary ID. 

You can find the complete list of acceptable IDs and more information on how to upgrade through https://www.paymaya.com/upgrade.', 'modified': '2019-09-13T01:54:06Z'}

