We apologize for the delayed responses. This was an issue before and, you may have noticed, we have been more active responding to reviews. üòä You can expect a response from our support@paymaya.com email team within 48hours. You may also contact us at PayMayaCares using the Messenger app.", 'modified': '2019-03-13T00:56:46Z'}
